[ctns_make id='gen_prop_eq_substitution_property_of_equality']

  [ctns_front style='']
Substitution Property Of Equality
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='']
For all real numbers $$x,y \in \mathbb{R},$$<br/> if $$x=y$$, then $$y$$ can be substituted for<br/>$$x$$ in any expression.
  [/ctns_back]  

  [ctns_backspeak]
For all real numbers X and Y, -- if x equals y -- then y can be substituted for x in any expression.
  [/ctns_backspeak]  

[/ctns_make]
